flowchart LR
    CHANGE[Engineering Change] --> LIB[Shared library]
    CHANGE --> API[API or service]
    CHANGE --> DATA[Schema or data path]

    LIB --> S1[Dependent service A]
    LIB --> S2[Dependent service B]
    API --> CLIENTS[Client applications]
    DATA --> JOBS[Analytics and batch jobs]

    S1 --> USERS[Users and customers]
    S2 --> USERS
    CLIENTS --> USERS
    JOBS --> REPORTS[Business and regulatory reports]

    USERS --> MONEY[Financial and operational impact]
    REPORTS --> COMPLIANCE[Compliance and legal impact]

    FLAGS[Feature flags and rollback] -. constrain .-> USERS
    OBS[Monitoring and detection] -. reduce duration .-> MONEY
